---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: RFA
mainClass: "page page--experience"
featuredProjects:
- CAVITATION
- HEI
- MACHINING
---


<section class="page-hero" style="--hero-img: url('/assets/images/experience/rfa/s1_engine_bay.jpg');">
    <div class="page-hero__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container page-hero__inner">
        <p class="page-hero__kicker">Internship</p>
        <h1 class="page-hero__title">Rocket Factory Augsburg AG</h1>
        <p class="page-hero__sub">Propulsion Department • 2025 • Augsburg, DE</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="story">
    <p class="page-disclamer">
        Non-Disclosure Agreement: I will only disclose non-proprietary information regarding my work at RFA. All
        images are public knowledge.
    </p>
    <div class="container story__grid">

        <figure class="media media--16x9">
            <video class="media__el" controls playsinline preload="metadata"
                poster="/assets/images/experience/rfa/video_cover.png">
                <source
                    src="/assets/images/experience/rfa/helix_test.mp4"
                    type="video/mp4">
            </video>
        </figure>


        <div class="story__content">
            <h2 class="story__title">Building Rockets Like Cars</h2>
            <p class="story__text">
                Rocket Factory Augsburg AG is one of the first commercial European companies developing orbital
                class launcher capable of delivering variety of payloads to different orbits.</p> 
                 <p class="story__text">
                    Its uniqueness stands in successful full in-house development of <strong>Europe's first oxygen-rich 
                    staged combustion (ORSC) engine </strong> called HELIX capable of delivering roughly 100kN of thrust.
            </p>
            <p class="story__text">
                <span> << Watch out! The 2023 HELIX IST campaign footage</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="story story--reverse">
    <div class="container story__grid">

        <figure class="media media--16x9">
            {% img "assets/images/experience/rfa/ignition.png", "Engine ignition" %}
            
        </figure>


        <div class="story__content">
            <h2 class="story__title">My Work</h2>
            <p class="story__text">
                As a part of propulsion R&D team I have made contributions in fields of fluid
                mechanics analysis on refinement and development of HELIX specificaly cavitation research on component testing.</p> 
                <p class="story__text">
            Key projects I have been involved in include:</p>
            <div class="education-text-bullets">
              <ul>
                <li>Iterations of system design</li>
                <li>Cavitation research of propellant/ignition feed system</li>
                <li>Development of test rigs for component testing</li>
                <li>Research based empirical data analysis.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</section>

